/home/palash/anaconda3/bin/../lib/libstdc++.so.6

body:
The problem is that anaconda is including libstdc++:
`/home/palash/anaconda3/bin/../lib/libstdc++.so.6`

You're building with your system libstdc++.so.6, but using an older version when trying to run it.
